parameters: [Principal] U-Um, are you here to make a payment today as well?
[Principal] It seems that today is different, isn't it? ♥

[Principal] Well... actually, you see... I've run out of contraceptives
and condoms.
[Anastasia] S-so... th-then... pl-please... hurry... haa... haa...

[Principal] (Oh... well, well♪ This is getting interesting, isn't it?
♥)

[Principal] (After being teased so much until now... It wouldn't be
interesting if we just continue normally like this, right?)

[Principal] As an educator, I believe that contraception is essential
in sexual education, you see ♪
[Principal] Well, after all, contraception is necessary, isn't it? ♪

[Principal] I also have a strong desire to have sex, but it would be
troublesome if I don't have any contraception.
[Anastasia] Haa...haa... Wh-what should I do? Haa...haa...

[Principal] If you could just go to the town... and buy some condoms
for me, that would be great♪

[Anastasia] You... said you would let me do it without protection...
*pant*... *pant*...

[Anastasia] M-Me... you want me to... do something like that...?
*pant*... *pant*...

[Principal] Oh my... If you don't want to, it's fine, you know? If you
don't want to.
[Principal] I believe condoms are sold at the lingerie shop in town...♪

[Principal] That Anastasia-sama... I can't believe she actually went to
buy condoms♥
[Principal] This laughter just won't stop♪ Hehehe
